The fourteenth chapter on cauterizing the stinking nose.	CHAPTER FOURTEEN. On cauterization for foetor of the nose.	0.7310343
If you treat him with what we mentioned in the classification and the treatment is not successful, then quickly give the sick person nutmeg for three nights. Then shave his head. And cauterize him with the middle cautery using the olive-shaped cautery iron. Then cauterize him with the nail-shaped cautery iron two cauterizations above the eyebrows slightly under the hair.	When you have treated foetor by those methods given in its section and your treatment is unsuccessful, give the patient laxative draughts for three days; then shave his head; and burn with a median cauterization with the olivary cautery; then cauterize him twice above the eyebrows a little below the hair with a claviform cautery.	0.84083426
And be careful of the artery, do not cut it.	Beware of cutting the artery.	0.6332793
